{"tid":890963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐努烏梁海係咪中國國土？ 北京高院：中國人無權知道","createTime":"2018-11-05T17:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T08:11:50.000Z","uid":35790,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ced2dbebc7652d03082d4a56bdc91c2e435fc905","tid":890963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:48:08.000Z","msg":"【好奇害死貓】唐努烏梁海係咪中國國土？ 北京高院：中國人無權知道<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181105/large/1541431667_9d8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181105%2Flarge%2F1541431667_9d8e.jpg&h=cb4b97d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181105/large/1541431680_e72c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181105%2Flarge%2F1541431680_e72c.png&h=73f83da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181105/large/1541431680_45ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181105%2Flarge%2F1541431680_45ef.png&h=90eecda2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事源去年8月15日，中國市民殷敏鴻向外交部申請政府訊息公開，問「1949年以後，中華人民共和國政府有沒有簽署過放棄中國國土（唐努烏梁海地區）的協議？」據內地網站資料顯示，唐努烏梁海屬於中國領土，1914年被沙俄佔領16.8604萬平方公里，現由俄羅斯管理，歷史上其他政府從未在法律上正式放棄俄佔唐努烏梁海的領土主權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國外交部於一個月後發出覆函稱，「根據《中華人民共和政府訊息公開條例》第14條和第21條，你申請的訊息涉密，不屬於政府訊息公開範疇。」</span>覆函還指，如不服答覆，可申請行政覆議，或向北京市第三中級人民法院提起行政訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n殷敏鴻遂於本年3月7日，向北京市第三中級人民法院起訴中國外交部。不過，法院並不受理，殷敏鴻一於「問到底」，再就不受理上訴，要求予以立案，但被駁回上訴。<br />\n<br />\n微信號「律酷法律」斥道：「這麼簡單問題，為甚麼搞的這麼複雜」，並推論出「1.外交部答覆：中國領土版圖涉密，中國人沒有權利知道。2.北京高院回答：外交部答覆正確，我們不管。中國的版圖中國人不能知道」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，「律酷法律」還提出，中國刑法第282條指出，非法獲取國家秘密的，處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役、管制或者剝奪政治權利；情節嚴重的，處3年以上7年以下有期徒刑。若中國人知道中國實際版圖，或可能會被追究刑事責任。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181106/58879139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58879139&d=DD0ZIIEfIDfASuvfVMNE3xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3913b6b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F58879139&h=2b06c321\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181106/58879139</a>"},{"pid":"6a7f5c6b976ead30742f51d7db3195bf5f26b324","tid":890963,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"國家機密<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c433cf4b18f4fabcc901f5cf626bc5f87bc147","tid":890963,"uid":4964,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"變相答左你囉"},{"pid":"59ba2730017a883f6a79072ad400f1b94d0485fe","tid":890963,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"中俄密約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53482d641bdce39648ed7010edda590c14d0e0c","tid":890963,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"62c433cf4b18f4fabcc901f5cf626bc5f87bc147","tid":890963,"uid":4964,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"變相答左你囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:54:00.000Z","msg":"有密約, <br />\n唔答得你無, 又唔答得你有, 因為係密約, 所以係機密<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b8c90b9d83152a391ac2a17a05d6e38dbda827","tid":890963,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:54:51.000Z","msg":"支那外交部真係無答錯<br />\n<br />\n有密約存在, 唔係咁答, 可以點答？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj